snippet.title: Once Human - Official Demo Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Here's a fresh look at the various bizarre enemies, gameplay, and more in this latest trailer for Once Human. Once Human is coming to PC, and a limited-time demo is available on Steam as part of Steam Next Fest. Once Human is a multiplayer open-world survival game set in a strange, post-apocalyptic future. Unite with friends to fight monstrous enemies, uncover secret plots, compete for resources, and build your own territory. Once, you were merely human. Now, you have the power to remake the world.

#Gaming #Games #GameTrailers
